      "span_text": "The Progressive Aerobic Cardiovascular Endurance Run (PACER) is a valid and reliable method for all ages and measured an individual's aerobic capacity.This test was administered according to the instructions outlined on the FITNESSGRAM CD (Cooper Institute for Aerobic Research, 2000)."
